<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>Gold wing</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>KUIPER/kuiper</FactionKey>
  <Description>Difficulty: &lt;color=green&gt;EASY&lt;/color&gt;

Gold Wing "Heaven Sent" consists of a 50mm/Beam Kasr and a trio of Kyves, two dedicated to point defense and one an anti-jamming boat. Gold Wing's goal in an engagement is to take an area and refuse to let it go. Using the ruggedness of the Kasr and the support network of the Kyves. When encountering Particularly stiff resistance Gold wing can count on a Salvo from the VLS-3 mounted on the Kasr's rear C4 to swing a fight or finish off a particularly tough targed.
  </Description>
  <ModDependencies>
    <unsignedLong>3649434947</unsignedLong>
  </ModDependencies>
  <SortOverrideOrder>3</SortOverrideOrder>
